name: ServerWorldCreationTest
description: Used to test that modded dimension types and dimensions are loaded on a clean dedicated server launch. To test, start a clean dedicated server (no level.dat), and validate that the dimension `server_world_creation_test:server_world_creation_test` exists. This can be done with the `execute in` command. For example: `execute in server_world_creation_test:server_world_creation_test run say working correctly` will say `working correctly` in the chat if successful.
